          <p>Choosing the right credit card can save you thousands of rupees every year while unlocking premium benefits like lounge access, travel insurance, and accelerated rewards. Our editorial team evaluates cards across multiple dimensions — annual fees, reward structures, welcome benefits, and customer satisfaction — to bring you the definitive list of the best credit cards for 2026.</p>
          <p>Whether you're a frequent traveller, an online shopping enthusiast, a fuel-heavy commuter, or someone looking for a no-fee everyday card, our curated picks below cover every major category so you can make a confident, informed choice.</p>

