            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Zero or Low Annual Fees:</strong> Many top cards offer lifetime free options or fee waivers on meeting annual spend thresholds</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Fuel Surcharge Waiver:</strong> Save 1% on every fuel transaction across all petrol pumps in India</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Comprehensive Insurance:</strong> Air accident cover up to ₹1 crore, lost card liability cover, and purchase protection on premium cards</li>
          </ul>

