          <h2>Eligibility for Best Credit Cards</h2>
          <p>Eligibility varies by card tier, but here are the general criteria banks evaluate when processing applications for top-rated cards:</p>

          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Age:</strong> Minimum 21 years for primary cardholders; add-on cards available from 18 years</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Income:</strong> ₹25,000+ monthly for mid-tier cards; ₹1 lakh+ for super-premium cards like Infinia or Diners Black</li>
