            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Employment:</strong> Salaried professionals, self-employed individuals, and business owners with stable income</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Existing Relationship:</strong> Pre-approved offers available if you hold a savings account or FD with the issuing bank</li>
